label.value: AUMC Infinity Observed Normalized by Surface Area

value.value: The area under the first moment curve (AUMC) extrapolated to infinity, based on the last observed concentration divided by the surface area.

label.value: AUMC Infinity Observed Normalized by Weight

value.value: The area under the first moment curve (AUMC) extrapolated to infinity, based on the last observed concentration divided by the weight.

label.value: AUMC Infinity Predicted Normalized by Body Mass Index

value.value: The area under the first moment curve (AUMC) extrapolated to infinity, based on the last predicted concentration divided by the body mass index.

label.value: AUMC Infinity Predicted Normalized by Dose

value.value: The area under the first moment curve (AUMC) extrapolated to infinity, based on the last predicted concentration divided by the dose.

label.value: AUMC Infinity Predicted Normalized by Surface Area

value.value: The area under the first moment curve (AUMC) extrapolated to infinity, based on the last predicted concentration divided by the surface area.

label.value: AUMC Infinity Predicted Normalized by Weight

value.value: The area under the first moment curve (AUMC) extrapolated to infinity, based on the last predicted concentration divided by the weight.

label.value: AUMC Over Dosing Interval Normalized by Body Mass Index

value.value: The area under the first moment curve (AUMC) for the defined interval between doses (TAU) divided by the body mass index.

label.value: AUMC Over Dosing Interval Normalized by Dose

value.value: The area under the first moment curve (AUMC) for the defined interval between doses (TAU) divided by the dose.

label.value: Childhood Spinal Cord Neoplasm

value.value: A benign or malignant neoplasm affecting the spinal cord during childhood.

label.value: AUMC Over Dosing Interval Normalized by Surface Area

value.value: The area under the first moment curve (AUMC) for the defined interval between doses (TAU) divided by the surface area.

label.value: AUMC Over Dosing Interval Normalized by Weight

value.value: The area under the first moment curve (AUMC) for the defined interval between doses (TAU) divided by the weight.

label.value: AURC All Normalized by Body Mass Index

value.value: The area under the excretion rate curve (AURC) from time zero to the last measurable rate divided by the body mass index.

label.value: AURC All Normalized by Dose

value.value: The area under the excretion rate curve (AURC) from time zero to the last measurable rate divided by the dose.

label.value: AURC All Normalized by Surface Area

value.value: The area under the excretion rate curve (AURC) from time zero to the last measurable rate divided by the surface area.

label.value: AURC All Normalized by Weight

value.value: The area under the excretion rate curve (AURC) from time zero to the last measurable rate divided by the weight.

label.value: AURC Dosing to Last Concentration Normalized by Body Mass Index

value.value: The area under the excretion rate curve (AURC) from time zero to the last measurable rate, divided by the body mass index.

label.value: AURC Dosing to Last Concentration Normalized by Dose

value.value: The area under the excretion rate curve (AURC) from time zero to the last measurable rate, divided by the dose.

label.value: AURC Dosing to Last Concentration Normalized by Surface Area

value.value: The area under the excretion rate curve (AURC) from time zero to the last measurable rate, divided by the surface area.

label.value: AURC Dosing to Last Concentration Normalized by Weight

value.value: The area under the excretion rate curve (AURC) from time zero to the last measurable rate, divided by the weight.

label.value: Systemic Mastocytosis

value.value: Systemic infiltration of extracutaneous sites by clonal mast cells, with or without evidence of skin involvement.

label.value: AURC from T1 to T2 Normalized by Body Mass Index

value.value: The area under the excretion rate curve (AURC) over the interval from T1 to T2 divided by the body mass index.

label.value: AURC from T1 to T2 Normalized by Dose

value.value: The area under the excretion rate curve (AURC) over the interval from T1 to T2 divided by the dose.

label.value: AURC from T1 to T2 Normalized by Surface Area

value.value: The area under the excretion rate curve (AURC) over the interval from T1 to T2 divided by the surface area.

label.value: AURC from T1 to T2 Normalized by Weight

value.value: The area under the excretion rate curve (AURC) over the interval from T1 to T2 divided by the weight.

label.value: AURC Infinity Observed Normalized by Body Mass Index

value.value: The area under the excretion rate curve (AURC) extrapolated to infinity, calculated using the observed value of the last excretion rate, divided by the body mass index.

label.value: AURC Infinity Observed Normalized by Dose

value.value: The area under the excretion rate curve (AURC) extrapolated to infinity, calculated using the observed value of the last excretion rate, divided by the dose.

label.value: AURC Infinity Observed Normalized by Surface Area

value.value: The area under the excretion rate curve (AURC) extrapolated to infinity, calculated using the observed value of the last excretion rate, divided by the surface area.

label.value: AURC Infinity Observed Normalized by Weight

value.value: The area under the excretion rate curve (AURC) extrapolated to infinity, calculated using the observed value of the last excretion rate, divided by the weight.

label.value: AURC Infinity Predicted Normalized by Body Mass Index

value.value: The area under the excretion rate curve (AURC) extrapolated to infinity, calculated using the predicted value of the last non-zero excretion rate, divided by the body mass index.

label.value: AURC Infinity Predicted Normalized by Dose

value.value: The area under the excretion rate curve (AURC) extrapolated to infinity, calculated using the predicted value of the last non-zero excretion rate, divided by the dose.

label.value: Paroxysmal Hypertension

value.value: Hypertension that presents intermittently.

label.value: AURC Infinity Predicted Normalized by Surface Area

value.value: The area under the excretion rate curve (AURC) extrapolated to infinity, calculated using the predicted value of the last non-zero excretion rate, divided by the surface area.

label.value: AURC Infinity Predicted Normalized by Weight

value.value: The area under the excretion rate curve (AURC) extrapolated to infinity, calculated using the predicted value of the last non-zero excretion rate, divided by the weight.

label.value: AUC All Normalized by Body Mass Index

value.value: The area under the curve (AUC) from the time of dosing to the time of the last observation divided by the body mass index, regardless of whether the last concentration is measurable or not.

label.value: Amount Recovered Normalized by Body Mass Index

value.value: The cumulative amount recovered from the specimen type, from dosing to end of the current collection interval divided by the body mass index.

label.value: Amount Recovered Normalized by Dose

value.value: The cumulative amount recovered from the specimen type, from dosing to end of the current collection interval divided by the dose.

label.value: Amount Recovered Normalized by Surface Area

value.value: The cumulative amount recovered from the specimen type, from dosing to end of the current collection interval divided by the surface area.

label.value: Amount Recovered Normalized by Weight

value.value: The cumulative amount recovered from the specimen type, from dosing to end of the current collection interval divided by the weight.

label.value: Average Concentration Normalized by Body Mass Index

value.value: AUCTAU divided by TAU and then divided by the body mass index.

label.value: Average Concentration Normalized by Dose

value.value: AUCTAU divided by TAU and then divided by the dose.

label.value: Average Concentration Normalized by Surface Area

value.value: AUCTAU divided by TAU and then divided by the surface area.

label.value: Recurrent Gastric Carcinoma

value.value: The reemergence of gastric carcinoma after a period of remission.

label.value: Average Concentration Normalized by Weight

value.value: AUCTAU divided by TAU and then divided by the weight.

label.value: Maximum Concentration Normalized by Body Mass Index

value.value: The maximum concentration occurring at Tmax, divided by the body mass index.

label.value: Maximum Concentration Normalized by Surface Area

value.value: The maximum concentration occurring at Tmax, divided by the surface area.

label.value: Maximum Concentration Normalized by Weight

value.value: The maximum concentration occurring at Tmax, divided by the weight.

label.value: Minimum Concentration Normalized by Body Mass Index

value.value: The minimum concentration between dose time and dose time plus Tau (at Tmin) divided by the body mass index.

label.value: Minimum Concentration Normalized by Dose

value.value: The minimum concentration between dose time and dose time plus Tau (at Tmin) divided by the dose.

label.value: Minimum Concentration Normalized by Surface Area

value.value: The minimum concentration between dose time and dose time plus Tau (at Tmin) divided by the surface area.

label.value: Minimum Concentration Normalized by Weight

value.value: The minimum concentration between dose time and dose time plus Tau (at Tmin) divided by the weight.
